220
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:39,320
and what not to do,

221
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:41,720
you should be cautious.

222
00:12:45,640 --> 00:12:46,120
I will.

223
00:12:54,960 --> 00:12:55,960
Anything else?

224
00:12:59,080 --> 00:12:59,760
