229
00:13:11,320 --> 00:13:12,320
Excuse me, Master.

230
00:13:19,880 --> 00:13:21,640
Do you have anything to add, Master?

231
00:13:26,400 --> 00:13:27,400
Tonight, His Majesty

232
00:13:28,520 --> 00:13:30,480
