236
00:13:39,560 --> 00:13:40,080
Yes.

237
00:14:01,280 --> 00:14:01,960
Your Majesty,

238
00:14:02,760 --> 00:14:05,200
Dazheng and Zhunian
are only a water area away.

239
00:14:06,160 --> 00:14:08,320
