267
00:15:10,040 --> 00:15:10,880
to decorate them.

268
00:15:20,280 --> 00:15:21,880
Since the princess was back,

269
00:15:22,120 --> 00:15:23,360
she has paid

270
00:15:23,560 --> 00:15:24,840
